long_description: SUP - the  third generation of world's best pigments for microblading, manual technique. Use in the field of PMU (working with a PMU device) is also possible - to do this, the wanted PhiBrows pigment has to be mixed with PhiThinner in order to dilute it. As a mixing tool we recommend PhiMixer.-Learn more about SUP pigments by clicking on the link below:http:www.phibrows.commicroblading-pigments-See more about Honey Effect in our pigments by clicking on the link below:https:www.youtube.comwatch?v=m_G6--lmsP0We are happy to announce that the SUPE generation is coming out soon!
